dcterms:description: EEG samples collected from 32 participants while watching 40 one-minute video clips. Each participant rated the video on scales of valence, arousal, dominance, and liking using a self-assessment manikin. The dataset consists of 1086 EEG samples labeled into two classes: low arousal and high arousal.
dcterms:title: DEAP dataset
